'''Filordian''' was the native language of the [[Filordus|Filordi]] species from [[Filordis/Legends|Filordis]]. Filordian lacked some of the consonant sounds in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], so when Filordi spoke Basic, they usually ignored these sounds. They also had a gravely voice when speaking Basic.<ref name="UAA" />

